simple function implementation

function($return_value, $arg0, ...)
--
A call B

STACK
|------------|  
| A's local  |
| variables  |
-------------- <---- old $SP
| return     |
| value      |
|------------|
| arguments  |
|------------|
| old $SP    |
|------------|  
| B's local  |
| variables  |
-------------- <---- current $SP

$SP += 
sizeof (B's return value)
sizeof (B's arguments)
sizeof ($SP)
sizeof (B's local variables)



